{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":75,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"路人","listener":null,"text":"原来是莫爷，想不到竟在这里碰上你，令叔呢？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":15,"line_end":15},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"令叔是莫为神医嘛！当年在襄阳城外，今叔仗义相助，连诊金都差点忘了收取，治好我们小公子进哥儿的怪病，还擒下马许然那奸贼，莫爷记不起了吗？","tone":"微笑","chapter":363,"line_start":23,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"记起啦！你叫……哈！你叫……","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":29,"line_end":29},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"我叫沙福，少爷和夫人不知多么感激令叔和莫爷，只苦于不知如何寻找你们。令叔呢？为何见不到他哩？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":31,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"家叔年纪大了，返南方家乡后便不愿再出来闯荡。哈！又会这么巧的，沙管家要去到那里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":35,"line_end":35},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"真可惜，像令叔这样精通医术的高人，又是人慈人悲的侠士。实在难遇难见。","tone":"无奈","chapter":363,"line_start":39,"line_end":39},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"沙管家过许了，但我莫……嘛：已得家叔真传，敢说没有十成也有九成心得。嘿！我现在赶看去找客船，改天再和沙管家聊天吧。请啦！","tone":"调侃","chapter":363,"line_start":43,"line_end":43},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"莫爷真的已得令叔医术的真传？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"我怎会骗你，但今趟又是谁生病？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":53,"line_end":53},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"今趟是老爷，莫爷懂否医治伤寒症呢？","tone":"担心","chapter":363,"line_start":55,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"这有何难，不过待我找得客船再说如何？","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":57,"line_end":57},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"莫爷要坐船到甚么地方去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":61,"line_end":61},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_sha_fu","text":"我想到长安去混混，看能否闯出一番医业来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":63,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"如此就不用找船，因为我们正好要往关中。莫爷请！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":65,"line_end":65}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_sha_fu","name":"沙福","alias":[],"identity":"沙家管家","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"沙家管家，四十多岁，似管家模样，曾受莫为神医诊治之恩","personality":{"traits":["感恩图报","殷勤周到","善于察言观色","忠诚","热情好客"],"speech_style":"恭敬有礼","temperament":"温和"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_sha_lao_ye","type":"主仆","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"忠心耿耿"},{"target":"char_cheng_bi_su","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"侍奉周到"},{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"请其医治老爷"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":15,"line_end":15,"text":"有人迎上来喜叫道"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":31,"line_end":31,"text":"我叫沙福"}]},{"id":"char_chen_lai_man","name":"陈来满","alias":[],"identity":"沙家护院师傅","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"白白胖胖的中年汉子，武功不弱，沙家护院负责人","personality":{"traits":["热情","直率","仗义","以貌取人","敬重高手"],"speech_style":"豪爽","temperament":"开朗"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":133,"line_end":133,"text":"其中一人大喜道"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":143,"line_end":143,"text":"这位是陈来满陈师傅"}]},{"id":"char_yun_gui","name":"云贵","alias":[],"identity":"沙家年轻武师","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"沙家年轻武师，曾与寇仲闲聊","personality":{"traits":["健谈","幽默","直率","热情","识大体"],"speech_style":"轻松","temperament":"开朗"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":185,"line_end":185,"text":"其中一个被人叫作云贵的年轻武师失笑道"}]},{"id":"char_jin_ge_er","name":"进哥儿","alias":[],"identity":"沙家小公子","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"沙家小少爷，精灵俊秀，酷肖乃母，曾被莫为神医治好怪病","personality":{"traits":["精灵俊秀","胆小","乖巧","可爱","聪慧"],"speech_style":"童声","temperament":"天真"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_cheng_bi_su","type":"亲属","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"母子情深"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":193,"line_end":193,"text":"还有进哥儿"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":195,"line_end":195,"text":"生得精灵俊秀，酷肖乃母"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_feng","name":"小凤","alias":[],"identity":"沙家俏婢","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"程碧素的侍女","personality":{"traits":["伶俐","忠心上司","机警","温婉","细心"],"speech_style":"轻声","temperament":"文静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":193,"line_end":193,"text":"俏婢小凤"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_sha_family","name":"沙家","type":"家族","location":"关中","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"关中商贾世家，家主患伤寒症，正举家迁往关中","source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":193,"line_end":193,"text":"沙家"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":76,"line_end":150,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"大汉","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"这位兄弟高姓大名，有没有甚么门派字号，到关中要干甚么事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵（弓辰春）","listener":null,"text":"告诉本人你是何方神圣？看看是否够资格向我问话？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":363,"line_start":79,"line_end":79},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"大汉","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"老兄你先给我到岸上来，否则这艘船绝不起锚开航。在江湖行走的都该是明白人，不会因一己之故累及其他乘客。","tone":"淡然","chapter":363,"line_start":83,"line_end":83},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"小人查伙，是弘农帮帮主盛南甫座下四虎之一，刚才言语得罪，是不想外人看穿我们的关系，弓爷万勿见怪。","tone":"无奈","chapter":363,"line_start":93,"line_end":93},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_cha_huo","text":"你怎认得弓某人呢？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":363,"line_start":97,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"下船再说。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":99,"line_end":99},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"弓爷请上车。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":101,"line_end":101},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"幸好截得弓爷，否则帮主怪罪下来，我查伙怎担当得起。","tone":"平静","chapter":363,"line_start":103,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"雷九指大爷与我们帮主有过命的交情，五天前他往关中时路经我们弘农帮的总坛，曾千叮万嘱要我们妥为招呼弓爷，还写下弓爷的绘像，所以我们能把弓爷认出来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":107,"line_end":107},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_cha_huo","text":"竟有此事？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":363,"line_start":119,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"弓爷放心，若连把弓爷弄进关内这区区小事亦办不到，我们弘农帮还能出来混吗？","tone":"得意","chapter":363,"line_start":123,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_cha_huo","speaker_name":"查伙","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"我们早想好让弓爷混进关中的万全之策，只要掩去弓爷脸上这道好比生招牌的刀疤，来个改名换姓，再换上不同身份的服饰，便可做计行事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":127,"line_end":127},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"护院","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"原来是莫兄弟，令叔莫为神医呢？","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"嘿！你好！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":363,"line_start":141,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这位是陈来满陈师傅！","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":143,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_chen_lai_man","text":"原来是陈师傅，想不到又在这里见面呢！","tone":"微笑","chapter":363,"line_start":145,"line_end":145}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_cha_huo","name":"查伙","alias":[],"identity":"弘农帮帮主盛南甫座下四虎之一","faction":"faction_hong_nong_bang","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"弘农帮四虎之一，奉雷九指之命拦截并护送弓辰春入关","personality":{"traits":["机警","忠诚","善于应变","办事稳妥","恭敬"],"speech_style":"谨慎","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_sheng_nan_fu","type":"主仆","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"忠实部下"},{"target":"char_lei_jiu_zhi","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"受其托付"},{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"奉命护送"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":93,"line_end":93,"text":"小人查伙，是弘农帮帮主盛南甫座下四虎之一"}]},{"id":"char_cheng_bi_su","name":"程碧素","alias":[],"identity":"沙家少夫人","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"沙家少夫人，端秀美丽，温柔婉约，感激莫为神医","personality":{"traits":["端秀美丽","温柔婉约","知书达理","感恩","娴淑"],"speech_style":"温婉","temperament":"柔和"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_sha_lao_ye","type":"亲属","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"夫妻"},{"target":"char_jin_ge_er","type":"亲属","intensity":100,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"母子"},{"target":"char_xiao_feng","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"侍女"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":155,"line_end":155,"text":"有女子娇呼"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":193,"line_end":193,"text":"少夫人程碧素"}]},{"id":"char_sha_lao_ye","name":"沙老爷","alias":[],"identity":"沙家家主","faction":"faction_sha_family","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"沙家家主，染患伤寒症，需高人医治","personality":{"traits":["患病","信任名医","重视人情","谨慎","体面"],"speech_style":"未知","temperament":"虚弱"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_cheng_bi_su","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"夫妻"},{"target":"char_sha_fu","type":"主仆","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"主仆"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":55,"line_end":55,"text":"今趟是老爷"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":193,"line_end":193,"text":"沙家少夫人程碧素"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_hong_nong_bang","name":"弘农帮","type":"武林门派","location":"弘农","sub_divisions":["四虎"],"one_line":"弘农地方帮会，帮主盛南甫，有四虎得力助手，与雷九指交好","source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":93,"line_end":93,"text":"弘农帮帮主盛南甫座下四虎之一"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":151,"line_end":225,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"少夫人","listener":null,"text":"竟遇上莫少侠，他叔叔呢？还不请他们进来。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":363,"line_start":155,"line_end":155},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"年轻男子","listener":null,"text":"他的医术行吗？若有甚么差错，大哥和二哥定不肯绕过我。","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":161,"line_end":161},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"少夫人","listener":"char_sha_young_man","text":"相公你不如先向婆婆请示，由她作主，那大伯和二伯便没话说哩！","tone":"温柔","chapter":363,"line_start":165,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_chen_lai_man","speaker_name":"陈来满","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"莫兄弟武技高明，是否传自令叔呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":169,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_chen_lai_man","text":"我莫……嘿！一身技艺，都是家叔传授，他常说我容颜丑陋，生性愚鲁，没有点技艺傍身，出来行走江湖会非常吃亏，哈！","tone":"调侃","chapter":363,"line_start":171,"line_end":171},{"speaker":"char_chen_lai_man","speaker_name":"陈来满","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"男儿最紧要是志向远大，像古时的子羽，出名貌丑，还不是拜相封侯，名传千古。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":177,"line_end":177},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_chen_lai_man","text":"不知子羽在娶妻方面，是否也称心如意？","tone":"调侃","chapter":363,"line_start":181,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_yun_gui","speaker_name":"云贵","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"做得宰相，当然是妻妾如云，莫老兄何用担心。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":363,"line_start":185,"line_end":185},{"speaker":"char_sha_fu","speaker_name":"沙福","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"莫兄请随我来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":189,"line_end":189},{"speaker":"char_cheng_bi_su","speaker_name":"程碧素","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"莫少侠旅途辛苦，请先到房内休息，得养足精神，再劳顿少侠为老爷治病。","tone":"温柔","chapter":363,"line_start":199,"line_end":199},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"大汉","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"你来找谁？","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":213,"line_end":213},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"我叫莫为，弘农帮的查伙介绍我来见田爷的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":217,"line_end":217},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"大汉","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄请随我来！","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":221,"line_end":221},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"中年男子","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄你是那个门派的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":227,"line_end":227},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"鄙人的剑法乃家父所传。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":231,"line_end":231},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"中年男子","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"令尊高姓大名？","tone":"疑问","chapter":363,"line_start":233,"line_end":233},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":null,"text":"家父莫一心，在巴蜀有点名气。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":235,"line_end":235},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"中年男子","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄！不是我田三堂不想用你，而是我们今趟要向盛帮主求援，皆因广盛行那方面人强马壮。所以我要的是真正的高手，否则只是害了莫兄。","tone":"严肃","chapter":363,"line_start":237,"line_end":241}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_tian_san_tang","name":"田三堂","alias":[],"identity":"兴昌隆老板卜万年的大女婿，专责保护运盐船队","faction":"faction_xing_chang_long","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"兴昌隆老板大女婿，武功不弱，专责保护运盐船队","personality":{"traits":["精明","谨慎","识货","重义","务实"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"严肃"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_bo_wan_nian","type":"亲属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"翁婿"},{"target":"char_sheng_nan_fu","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"求援关系"},{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"招揽为武师"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":237,"line_end":237,"text":"不是我田三堂不想用你"},{"chapter":363,"line_start":263,"line_end":263,"text":"田三堂点头道"}]},{"id":"char_bo_wan_nian","name":"卜万年","alias":[],"identity":"兴昌隆商号老板","faction":"faction_xing_chang_long","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"兴昌隆商号老板，与秦王李世民一系关系密切","personality":{"traits":["商贾","谨慎","重利","识时务","面临强敌