{"segment":4,"line_start":226,"line_end":302,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_tian_san_tang","text":"田爷放心，盛帮主既敢介绍来见田爷，自然对我的剑法信心十足，田爷可向查伙兄查问清楚。","tone":"微笑","chapter":363,"line_start":255,"line_end":255},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄与盛帮主是甚么关系？","tone":"严肃","chapter":363,"line_start":259,"line_end":259},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_tian_san_tang","text":"盛帮主的拜把兄弟是我的亲叔。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":261,"line_end":261},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄请随我来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":363,"line_start":263,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":null,"text":"给我拿棍来。","tone":"厉声","chapter":363,"line_start":265,"line_end":265},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄请出招。不用留手。","tone":"严肃","chapter":363,"line_start":269,"line_end":269},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"莫兄试攻我看看！","tone":"激动","chapter":363,"line_start":289,"line_end":289},{"speaker":"char_tian_san_tang","speaker_name":"田三堂","listener":"char_xu_zi_ling","text":"难怪盛帮主会把莫兄推荐给我兴昌隆，得莫兄如此人才相助，还怕他甚么顾天璋，莫兄今天请随船队入关，田三堂定不会薄待于你。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":363,"line_start":295,"line_end":295}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_gu_tian_zhang","name":"顾天璋","alias":[],"identity":"广盛行大老板","faction":"faction_guang_sheng_xing","role":"villain","archetype":"npc","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"广盛行大老板，有唐室太子系撑腰，以武力威吓兴昌隆","personality":{"traits":["嚣张","强势","好斗","倚仗权势","贪婪"],"speech_style":"强硬","temperament":"跋扈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_li_jian_cheng","type":"合作者","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"太子系势力"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[363],"source_refs":[{"chapter":363,"line_start":295,"line_end":295,"text":"还怕他甚么顾天璋"},{"chapter":363,"line_sta